  <div class="c-entry-hero__content l-segment l-feature">
    
    
    <h1 class="c-page-title">Trump’s Iran whisperer</h1>

    <p class="c-entry-summary p-dek">He’s Trump’s guy on Iran, and he’s remaking the State Department in the president’s image.</p>

    <div class="c-byline">
  <span class="c-byline-wrapper">
    
      
