</source></picture>

      
    </span>
    
  </span>
  
    <span class="e-image__meta">
      
        <figcaption>Then Secretary of State Rex Tillerson during a United Nations Security Council meeting concerning North Korea’s nuclear ambitions on December 15, 2017.</figcaption>
      
      
